Package: heartbeatr
Type: Package
Title: A Workflow to Process Data Collected with PULSE Systems (Electricblue.eu)
Version: 0.0.0.9100
Authors@R: c(
    person("Rui", "Seabra", , "ptruimar@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0240-3992")),
    person("Fernando", "Lima", , "fplima@gmail.com", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9575-9834"))
           )
Description: Given one or multiple paths to files produced by a PULSE multi-channel 
    system (electricblue.eu/pulse) from a single experiment:
    [1] check pulse files for inconsistencies and read/merge all data,
    [2] split across time windows,
    [3] interpolate and smooth to optimize the raw data,
    [4] compute the heart rate frequency for each channel/window.
    Heart rate frequency is calculated using the XXXX algorithm.
